---
const siteTitle = "Hello World";
---

<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>{siteTitle} | State / Action</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 min-h-screen p-4 md:p-12 font-mono selection:bg-blue-100 selection:text-blue-700">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex flex-col min-h-screen">
      <header class="flex items-center justify-between py-6 border-b border-slate-200 mb-10">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-900 italic">
            Hello World
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] mt-2">
            Minimal Tailwind Sandbox
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="px-5 py-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full text-xs md:text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-blue-300 hover:text-blue-600 transition-all shadow-sm"
        >
          ← 作者のページへ
        </a>
      </header>

      <main class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center">
        <section
          class="w-full bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 border border-slate-100 px-8 py-12 md:px-12 md:py-16 text-center space-y-6"
        >
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">
            Hello, World
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
            シンプルな「Hello World」
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto">
            このページは、Tailwind CSS ベースのレイアウトやコンポーネントの雰囲気をテストするための、極めてシンプルなサンドボックスです。
          </p>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mt-4 px-5 py-3 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-slate-50 text-xs md:text-sm font-mono">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_0_3px_rgba(16,185,129,0.35)]"></span>
            <span class="uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-slate-300">Status</span>
            <span class="font-bold">OK — Ready to build</span>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 text-[11px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <span class="uppercase tracking-[0.25em] font-black">
          State / Action
        </span>
        <span>2026 · Hello World Test Page</span>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

